headline: After Hitting an  All-Time High, Is T-Mobile US Stock Still a Good Buy?
summary: T-Mobile US (NASDAQ: TMUS) is a top telecom stock that's been on a tear.  Let's take a closer look at how T-Mobile has been doing and whether it's still a good buy today.  What has made T-Mobile a popular telecom stock to own in recent years is its pursuit of growth and differentiating itself from its peers, referring to itself as the "un-carrier" brand.
